<HEADLINE> Russia Wants to Develop Ties with Germany and EU </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BERLIN, February 1 (Xinhua) -- Russia seeks a "dynamic and
constructive cooperation" with Germany, Russian Foreign Minister
Igor Ivanov said in Bonn on Monday.
</P>
<P>
At a press conference after meeting German Chancellor Gerhard
Schroeder, Ivanov said he expected Schroeder's forthcoming visit
to Moscow to provide a fresh impulse for the growth of bilateral
