contribute 4 million Canadian dollars (2.64 million U.S. dollars)
over five years for the project which will enable cacao and coffee
producers to adapt their business, for example by adopting new
procedures for managing information, negotiating contracts with
buyers and controlling coffee and cacao production operations.
</P>
<P>
