<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, February 1 (Xinhua) -- U.S President Bill Clinton
is to meet his foreign policy advisers on Monday to discuss how to
bring about a peace deal in Kosovo and the possibility of U.S.
troops going there, White House spokesman David Leavy said.
</P>
