<HEADLINE> Explosion Takes Place at Ford Plant Power Station in U.S. </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, February 1 (Xinhua) -- An explosion and fire rocked
a generating station for a huge Ford Motor Company plant in
Dearborn of Michigan State in the United States Monday, injuring
more than a dozen people, some seriously.
</P>
