<HEADLINE> Saint Lucian Prime Minister Extols Friendship (2) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Anthony noted that Caribbean countries are former colonial
countries which fully understand the meaning of national
sovereignty. He said the understanding fully reflects the
aspiration of people to be united.
</P>
<P>
Anthony stressed that Saint Lucia pursues the "one China"
policy and sees no reason why China's mainland should not be
reunited with Taiwan.
</P>
<P>
