an active role in economic globalization and the formation of a
new world economic order. China's efforts to help relax the Asian
financial crisis has not only benefited Asian countries, but also
small countries like Saint Lucia.
</P>
<P>
Anthony said China and Saint Lucia signed an economic and
technological cooperation agreement during the visit. He expressed
the belief that bilateral relations should not simply be
determined by political relations, but instead in terms of
cooperation at all levels. Anthony cited the vast potential for
broad cooperation and said Saint Lucia welcomes Chinese investment.
"China has opened its door to us and we will reciprocate," said
Anthony. 
