Saint Lucia-China relations is that China, as a big country, can
sincerely treat Saint Lucia, a small nation.
</P>
<P>
He expressed his thanks for China's support to his country.
</P>
<P>
Anthony stressed that Saint Lucia's adherence to the One China
policy is his country's sacred commitment, and the country will
never change its stance.
