<HEADLINE> Japan Claims Men's Giant Slalom at Winter Asiad </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
YONGPYONG, South Korea, February 2 (Xinhua) -- Japanese Join
Kawaguchi avenged his opening day loss to South Korean rival Hur
Seung-woo by claiming the men's giant slalom title at the Asian
Winter Games on Tuesday.
</P>
<P>
The 24-year-old Kawaguch, who was beaten into second place at
Sunday's Super-G slalom which won by Hur, turned the tide in today'
