taking the bronz in 2:37.41 and Choi Moon-Sung coming in fourth
in 2:38.74.
</P>
<P>
Kawaguchi's wind-aided second round skiing, clocking one minute
21.64 seconds, gave him the edge over Hur, who posted best first
round time of 1:13.02 but was dragged down by much slower second
round result of 1:22.95. 
