<HEADLINE> URGENT 19 Die in Angola's Plane Crash </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LUANDA, February 2 (Xinhua) -- At least 19 people were killed
early Tuesday in a plane crash in Cazenga, the Angolan capital's
most populous community, authorities said.
</P>
<P>
They said the plane was an Antonov-12 craft. 
</P>
