<HEADLINE> Kazakstan Wins Cross-coutry Relay, Third Gold At Asiad </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
YONGPYONG, South Korea, February 2 (Xinhua) -- Kazakhstan
quartet defended their title on Tuesday in the men's cross country
4x10 kilometers relay at the Kangwon Asain Winter Games.
</P>
<P>
