general manager Jerry West said Monday. "But there would be an
awful lot to talk about it internally before we'd do something
like that."
</P>
<P>
Shaquille O'Neal said he dislikes Rodman, even though the
Lakers need a power forward.
</P>
<P>
"I would not want to go against my big man," coach Del Harris
said. "I have the highest regard for the abilities of the guy who
could win the rebounding title seven years in a row and who has
been on two different championship teams as many times as he has."
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
</DOC>
